reviewText: My favorite! I watch this over and over! I am addicted. Every song is awesome and the guys do a fantastic job  I can't say enough about this. The product was delivered on time and in good order.  However, I was made to feel foolish by this purchase -- we very much enjoy Celtic Thunder,  BUT this product was renamed and re dated so as to appear new when it was the same one that was released years earlier and which I  had bought under another name.  I now have two copies of this very wonderful work, but I feel ripped off!

I have been a fan of Celtic Thunder since I first saw them appear on TV. I am still a fan and will continue to buy their cd & dvd's. Even though 3 of the original members have left, they still put good wholesome music that can be and will be a joy to listen too!!!! Thank you frances comer

I just don't understand why CT thinks they have to do this... re-release SOS with a different cover.  They have NO faith in their fan base.  I will GLADLY spend my hard-earned money buying CT, they don't have to rip the public off this way. It makes me mad.  This is not the first time I've been deceived this way, by SOS with a slightly different title.  Fortunately I have a few friends who've not yet had the pleasure of CT, so I can pass these on, as gifts, but it makes me upset that the marketing folks for CT think they need to stoop to this behavior.
